{"tid":2142551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"孟買貧民窟逾半有武肺抗體","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T13:08:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2a81fb91c8e259af34f901648eb85974d47113","tid":2142551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:04:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200730/OTEFF25VBE2KE24BHVUNOT3QLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200730%2FOTEFF25VBE2KE24BHVUNOT3QLA%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=2859f66c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200730%2FOTEFF25VBE2KE24BHVUNOT3QLA%2F&h=f4e31ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200730/OTEFF25VBE2KE24BHVUNOT3QLA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n孟買貧民窟逾半有武肺抗體<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9FE-duN2vjH2Qq02vjJrVdmnx9s=/640x394/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S2B2KVIW2ILROCCHRTTVYQBMJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9FE-duN2vjH2Qq02vjJrVdmnx9s%3D%2F640x394%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS2B2KVIW2ILROCCHRTTVYQBMJU.jpg&h=4c9e7dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孟買市政府據報有派人在全市狂灑一種抗瘧疾噴劑。<br />\n<br />\n印度孟買官方研究發現，貧民窟逾半居民對武漢肺炎病毒有抗體，非貧民窟居民只16%有抗體，令外界再次質疑官方統計數據的真確性，並懷疑疫情正放緩的孟買是否已達致群體免疫。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：俄涉利用假疫情打擊美大選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方數據再受質疑<br />\n<br />\n孟買市政府與智庫和研究所共同進行調查，隨機抽出6,936人進行血液測試，發現在共有近150萬人居住的達拉維、商波爾和馬塔蓋三個貧民窟中，有57%居民有病毒抗體。調查發現無症狀感染者「似乎在所有感染個案中佔很高比例」，而且病毒致命率似乎「很低」，僅千分之一至2,000分之一；但結果亦指向病毒以較早前估計更大的規模在貧民窟擴散，居民共用廁所等設施或是感染率高的部份原因，顯示人口密集對傳播十分關鍵。專家相信今次檢測樣本「在數據上堅實」和具代表性。<br />\n<br />\n孟買市政府進行調查的前一周，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"23a60ffae01d91b03db19335ab65d64a2f074384","tid":2142551,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:08:54.000Z","msg":"【飛雲】影一張相等於7000蚊嘅時代來臨了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}